<!DOCTYPE html>
<html class="no-js" lang="">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<title>01 - Basics</title>
		<meta name="description" content="" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ '/css/common.css' | url }}">
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ '/css/web-api-01.css' | url }}">
	</head>

	<body>
		<main id="content">
			<code class="breadcrumbs">
				<a href="{{ '/' | url }}">&larr; Animation</a> / <a href="{{ '../ '}}">Web API</a>
			</code>
			<div class="container">
				<h1>01 Basics</h1>
				<code class="breadcrumbs">
					<a href="https://github.com/nathanlong/animation/blob/main/css/web-api-01.css">CSS Source</a>
					|
					<a href="https://github.com/nathanlong/animation/blob/main/js/web-api-01.js">JS Source</a>
				</code>

				<p>Buttons to control the play/pause of the animation as well as the playback speed.</p>

				<div id="animation-target"></div>

				<div class="animation-controls">
					<button id="spin">Spin Me Right Round (Play)</button>
					<button id="speed-up">Speed Up</button>
					<button id="reset">Slow Down</button>
					<button id="stop">Stop</button>
				</div>
				<div class="animation-controls">
					<button id="mouse-bind">Bind Speed and Scale to Mouse Position</button>
					<small>(You'll have to reload after using this...)</small>
				</div>
			</div>
		</main>

		<script src="{{ '/js/web-api-01.js' | url }}"></script>
	</body>
